OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772679804
OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FThe US-Israeli war on Iran has entered
OL,8,Fits sixth day as flights carrying
OL,9,FBritons left stranded in the Middle
OL,10,FEast amid the conflict are due to
OL,11,Farrive in the UK.
OL,13,FThe first Government rescue flight and
OL,14,FBritish Airways commercial flight from
OL,15,FMuscat were expected to land in the UK
OL,16,Fearly on Thursday.
OL,18,FIt comes after the US and Israel
OL,19,Fintensified their bombing attacks
OL,20,Fagainst Iran's military and security
OL,21,Fapparatus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772679804
OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer's Government has continued to
OL,9,Fdefend the status of the special
OL,10,Frelationship with the US after a
OL,11,Fseries of attacks from President
OL,12,FDonald Trump.
OL,14,FAnd Cyprus said that a British
OL,15,Fpresence is "the least we expect" as a
OL,16,Fwarship being readied to protect the
OL,17,FBritish base there is not set to sail
OL,18,Funtil next week.
OL,26,@wD@MOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772679804
OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FMuscat, which is some 300 miles by
OL,8,Froad from Dubai and Abu Dhabi, has
OL,9,Femerged as a key location for people
OL,10,Fto leave the Middle East as the vast
OL,11,Fmajority of commercial flights from
OL,12,Fthe United Arab Emirates are cancelled
OL,13,Fdue to airspace restrictions caused by
OL,14,Fthe conflict.
OL,16,FSir Keir announced two further
OL,17,FGovernment-chartered flights, one of
OL,18,Fwhich is expected to leave Oman on
OL,19,FThursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772679804
OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FTwo more British Airways flights will
OL,8,Ftake passengers from Muscat to London
OL,9,FHeathrow on Friday and Saturday.
OL,11,FSome 138,000 British nationals have
OL,12,Fregistered their presence in the
OL,13,FMiddle East.
OL,15,FSir Keir has told MPs the special
OL,16,Frelationship with Washington will
OL,17,Fendure after the US president lashed
OL,18,Fout at his initial refusal to allow
OL,19,FBritish bases to be used for raids
OL,20,Fagainst Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772679804
OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FAfter Mr Trump said the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fwas "not Winston Churchill", Sir Keir
OL,9,Fsaid the bond with the US was not
OL,10,Fabout "hanging on to President Trump's
OL,11,Flatest words".
OL,13,FHe defended his decisions about the
OL,14,Fuse of UK bases, saying the country
OL,15,Fneeds to act "with clarity, with
OL,16,Fpurpose, and with a cool head".
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@[O]rD@GOUsD@MO]wD@NOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
