PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772679804
OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FIn response to Iran's retaliatory
OL,8,Factions, Sir Keir has given the US
OL,9,Fpermission to use British bases for
OL,10,Fthe limited purpose of attacking
OL,11,Fmissile launchers and infrastructure,
OL,12,Fbut RAF jets have not been involved in
OL,13,Fstriking Iran.
OL,15,FWestern officials said on Wednesday
OL,16,Fthat US bombers had not yet used Diego
OL,17,FGarcia in the Indian Ocean or RAF
OL,18,FFairford in Gloucestershire, but that
OL,19,Fthe UK was ready to accept them and
OL,20,Fthat they were expected to arrive
OL,21,Fwithin the next few days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772679804
OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FDeputy Prime Minister David Lammy said
OL,8,Fthe UK and US are "close allies" but
OL,9,Fthat the US has chosen a "different
OL,10,Fway".
OL,12,F"The US has chosen a different way,
OL,13,Fand we have made an assessment, and
OL,14,Fit's the right assessment, about not
OL,15,Fputting UK soldiers into an offensive
OL,16,Fsituation that did not meet the legal
OL,17,Fthreshold that we set in our own
OL,18,Fcountry," he told ITV's Peston.
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@`O]qD@ZOUrD@DO]tD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
