OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FThe Government has also been
OL,8,Fcriticised for failing to have enough
OL,9,Fmilitary assets in the Middle East
OL,10,Fregion after RAF Akrotiri in Cyprus
OL,11,Fwas hit by a drone.
OL,13,FAir defence destroyer HMS Dragon will
OL,14,Fbe sent to the eastern Mediterranean
OL,15,Fto help protect Cyprus, but the Type
OL,16,F45 warship is not expected to sail
OL,17,Funtil next week.
OL,19,FSir Keir said Wildcat helicopters with
OL,20,Fanti-drone capabilities would be on
OL,21,Fthe Mediterranean island this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
