SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772679804
OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FHe insisted action had been taken in
OL,8,Fresponse to rising tensions in the
OL,9,Fregion before the war broke out.
OL,11,FThe Cypriot high commissioner to the
OL,12,FUK, Kyriacos Kouros, said the
OL,13,Fdeployment of HMS Dragon was welcome
OL,14,Fbut noted it would take "more than a
OL,15,Fweek" to arrive.
OL,26,@vD@YOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
