OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FAsked if he thought the UK had acted
OL,8,Fwith sufficient urgency to protect
OL,9,Fthose people who are living in and
OL,10,Faround the bases, he told Sky News:
OL,11,F"Already we have the presence of Greek
OL,12,Fforces on the island. Two frigates
OL,13,Farrived, four aircraft arrived, all of
OL,14,Fthem with abilities to combat drones.
OL,16,F"The French are coming. So... the
OL,17,Fleast we expect is the Britons to also
OL,18,Fbe present since, as I said, we are
OL,19,Fnot only defending Cypriots on the
OL,20,Fisland."
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
