OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FFrance has sent its flagship nuclear-
OL,8,Fpowered aircraft carrier the Charles
OL,9,Fde Gaulle to the region, accompanied
OL,10,Fby its air wing, and its escorting
OL,11,Ffrigates in response to the strike on
OL,12,FRAF Akrotiri.
OL,14,FElsewhere, the UK Maritime Trade
OL,15,FOperations Centre (UKMTO) said it had
OL,16,Freceived reports of an incident near
OL,17,FMubarak Al-Kabeer in Kuwait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
