OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,F"The Master of a tanker at anchor,
OL,8,Freports witnessing and hearing a large
OL,9,Fexplosion on the port side, then
OL,10,Fseeing a small craft leave the
OL,11,Fvicinity," it said in a statement.
OL,13,F"There is oil in the water coming from
OL,14,Fa cargo tank which could have some
OL,15,Fenvironmental impact, the vessel has
OL,16,Ftaken on water, there are no fires
OL,17,Freported and the crew are safe and
OL,18,Fwell. Authorities are investigating."
OL,20,FIn other developments on Wednesday:
