OL,3,CIran war enters sixth day as flights
OL,4,Cdue to bring Britons home from Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,F` Iran's ambassador Seyed Ali Mousavi
OL,8,Fwas summoned by the UK Government.
OL,10,F` A US submarine sank an Iranian
OL,11,Fwarship in the Indian Ocean.
OL,13,F` Iran continued to launch attacks at
OL,14,Fcountries across the region, with
OL,15,FSaudi Arabia and Kuwait targeted with
OL,16,Fmissiles and drones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
